    dc:creator "Shin, Bora; Choi, Sei-Woong; Kim, Sung-Soo" ;
    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "Fourteen new records of Crambidae (Lepidoptera) from South Korea" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6786073>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6786079>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6786083> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6786073>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Adults of 14 species newly recorded from Korea. Scale bar=5 mm. A. Paracymoriza distinctalis, B. Pseudocatharylla duplicellus, C. Psammotis orientalis, D. Anania albeoverbascalis, E. Anania stachydalis, F. Ecpyrrhorrhoe rubiginalis, G. Scoparia iwasakii, H. Haritalodes basipunctalis, I. Nagiella inferior, J. Notarcha aurolinealis, K. Herpetogramma okamotoi, L. Glyphodes formosanus, M. Mecyna fusei, and N. Udea tritalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6786073/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6786079>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Male genitalia of the Crambidae from Korea. Scale bar = 1mm (A, E, G, I, K), 0.5mm (B, C, D. F, H, J, L). A, B. Paracymoriza distinctalis; C, D. Pseudocatharylla duplicellus; E, F. Anania albeoverbascalis; G, H. Scoparia iwasakii; I, J. Haritalodes basipunctalis; K, L. Nagiella inferior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6786079/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6786083>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Female genitalia of the Crambidae from Korea. Scale bar = 1mm. A. Paracymoriza distinctalis, B. Pseudocatharylla duplicellus, C. Psammotis orientalis, D. Anania albeoverbascalis, E. Anania stachydalis, F. Ecpyrrhorrhoe rubiginalis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6786083/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

